data.description: DON'T MISS THE OPPORTUNITY TO OWN A NEXT-GEN MASTERPIECE IN SOLA VISTA!!!  A separate entrance will take you to the in-law suite with a living room,  kitchen, bedroom, and full bathroom, making it ideal for a multi-generational family, or to generate extra income.   The main house features an open concept with a beautiful kitchen that connects the living room and dining area ideal to be connected with your loved ones while you are cooking or having parties. You can experience breathtaking sunset seating on the porch while you are sipping wine or coffee.  Outside you can enjoy the community amenities the relaxing pool and the kid's park to enjoy a weekend full of fun with your family.  Located 20 min from Lake Nona Medical City and Saint Cloud Lakefront Park. 40 minutes from Disney and other theme parks.
